SUMMARY:Hopewell House Grief Support: Community Grief Ritual
DESCRIPTION:Category: Peer Support\nCost: FREE\nFormat: In-person\, drop-in
 \, no RSVP needed\nInfo: A practice of transforming individual and collect
 ive grief within a supportive community. All grief is welcome.\nAddress: 6
 171 SW Capitol Highway\, Portland\, OR 97239\nPhone: 503-894-7560\nWebsite
 : https://hopewellhousepdx.org/grief-support/\nDetails: Free grief support
  in a beautiful\, peaceful setting. The monthly Community Grief Ritual is 
 the most accessible entry point - drop-in\, no RSVP. Grief groups run in 6
 -session series with registration. Hopewell House is primarily a residenti
 al end-of-life care facility that also offers community grief services.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN"><HTML><BODY><p><strong>Category:</strong> Peer Support</p><p><strong>Cost:</strong> FREE</p><p><strong>Format:</strong> In-person, drop-in, no RSVP needed</p><p>A practice of transforming individual and collective grief within a supportive community. All grief is welcome.</p><p><strong>Address:</strong> 6171 SW Capitol Highway, Portland, OR 97239</p><p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:503-894-7560">503-894-7560</a></p><p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://hopewellhousepdx.org/grief-support/">https://hopewellhousepdx.org/grief-support/</a></p><p><strong>Details:</strong> Free grief support in a beautiful, peaceful setting. The monthly Community Grief Ritual is the most accessible entry point - drop-in, no RSVP. Grief groups run in 6-session series with registration. Hopewell House is primarily a residential end-of-life care facility that also offers community grief services.</p></BODY></HTML>
